snippet.title: Loddlenaut - Gameplay Trailer | Wholesome Snack: The Game Awards Edition
snippet.description: Clean the polluted ocean and help revive the planet in Loddlenaut. Pick up trash, recycle materials, and befriend adorable critters called Loddles in this cozy underwater title. A Steam demo is now available.
